1
00:01:32,210 --> 00:01:34,940
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:39,940
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,020
His Majesty didn't attend court yesterday.

4
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:52,170
Is he not attending today either?

5
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,039
I've heard that

6
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,840
not only was Her Majesty
severely injured,

7
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,170
but even His Majesty...

8
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,270
If that's true,

9
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:04,760
how can we possibly compete
against Prince Duan's faction?

10
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,640
All right.

11
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:08,360
Both of you, keep your voices down.

12
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,960
Don't frighten yourselves.

13
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,240
Lord Jia.

14
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,710
From what I've heard,

15
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,120
His Majesty

16
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:19,150
will not be able to come,

17
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,540
as we expected.

18
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:24,120
This is precisely

19
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,850
our golden opportunity to rise to power.

20
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:28,280
But why isn't

21
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:30,570
Prince Duan showing his face?

22
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,910
You're asking me?

23
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,000
Who should I ask then?

24
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,590
Prince Duan trusts you the most.

25
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:40,100
His Highness also trusted Zhao Wucheng.

26
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:40,840
Wasn't he

27
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:44,070
assassinated at the street corner
yesterday?

28
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,120
Lord Zhao is dead?

29
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:53,560
Today's court session

30
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:56,120
is like walking into a trap.

31
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,180
We might not be able

32
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,030
to stay alive.

33
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:05,030
Lord Mu's scheme

34
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,240
has put us in a terrible position.

35
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:53,190
I haven't practiced my makeup skills
for a long time.

36
00:03:53,190 --> 00:03:53,910
I'm rusty.

37
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,530
Let me do your makeup again.

38
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,040
That's enough, Wanyin.

39
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:01,440
You've already redone it once.

40
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,470
Are you tired?

41
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:05,750
Not at all.

42
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,840
I think it looks quite good now.

43
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,600
I don't look as haggard anymore.

44
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,040
No.

45
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,310
In court,

46
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,750
dozens of eyes will be watching you,

47
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,980
each person with countless schemes.

48
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,570
We absolutely cannot let them
spot any flaws.

49
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,740
Maybe you shouldn't attend court today.

50
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,730
Let's delay for a few more days.

51
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,980
If the treaty is signed one day later,

52
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:48,290
it gives our enemies
one more day to counterattack.

53
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:51,800
By the time Xiahou Bo realizes
what's happening,

54
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,290
we won't have the lead anymore.

55
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:55,270
But...

56
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,130
I know you're worried about my health,

57
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:58,890
but look,

58
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:02,430
the wound has stopped bleeding.

59
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:08,150
If such a powerful poison
couldn't kill me,

60
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,040
attending court

61
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,700
is nothing to worry about.

62
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:14,910
Your Majesty,

63
00:05:14,910 --> 00:05:16,240
Physician Xiao is here.

64
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,510
If you don't trust me,

65
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,690
surely you'll trust

66
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,610
Physician Xiao's opinion?

67
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,530
Physician Xiao,

68
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,600
tell the Noble Consort—

69
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:39,560
my wound

70
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,580
is healing well, isn't it?

71
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:48,060
Your Majesty's wound is indeed healing.

72
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,960
Some moderate activity

73
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:52,510
would help with blood circulation.

74
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:54,920
See?

75
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,420
Then make it quick.

76
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,500
I'll wait for you here.

77
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,560
That won't do.

78
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:11,240
While I'm pretending at court,

79
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:14,010
you need to go comfort the ladies
in the harem.

80
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:16,040
We have to make it look real.

81
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,360
Xie Yong'er did say

82
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,760
that in these three days,

83
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:22,950
my Zhaoyang Palace

84
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:25,360
is being trampled upon
by all those women of yours.

85
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:27,690
Then go quickly. What are you waiting for?

86
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,560
I still need Physician Xiao
to change my dressing.

87
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,600
I'm worried that—

88
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,570
How about

89
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,510
you help me change it?

90
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:40,120
No one wants to help you with that.

91
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,850
I'm leaving.

92
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,360
Your Majesty!

93
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,159
Your Majesty.

94
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:57,990
Your Majesty.

95
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,050
Physician Xiao.

96
00:07:04,530 --> 00:07:06,170
I have a favor to ask of you.

97
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,990
Please speak, Your Majesty.

98
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,870
Is there any strong medicine

99
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,200
that can quickly

100
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,560
boost energy and spirit?

101
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:28,310
His Majesty arrives!

102
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:04,040
Long live Your Majesty.

103
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,120
Rise, my dear ministers.

104
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,830
Thank you, Your Majesty.

105
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,310
Your Majesty,

106
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,400
after the trip to Mount Bei,

107
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:20,410
we heard
the Empress Dowager suddenly fell ill.

108
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,410
However, when we

109
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:23,870
tried to visit, we were all turned away.

110
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:24,870
Now,

111
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,930
three days have passed,

112
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:29,830
and rumors spread throughout the court

113
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,330
that the Empress Dowager didn't fall ill.

114
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,059
Then what is it?

115
00:08:36,549 --> 00:08:37,280
It's that...

116
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:42,080
she was assassinated
by the Yan State envoys!

117
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,929
Assassination?

118
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,960
How did you know?

119
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,290
Those Yan people

120
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,450
massacred over

121
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:50,970
50 of our soldiers
in front of the posthouse.

122
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,150
Then they vanished without a trace.

123
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:53,840
If not them,

124
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,280
who else could it be?

125
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,400
Lord Mu is truly well-informed.

126
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:02,210
You even know the exact number

127
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,630
of fallen soldiers.

128
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,520
That's right.

129
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,200
The Empress Dowager didn't fall ill.

130
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,130
She was attacked by conspirators.

131
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,030
After the shock,

132
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,050
she suddenly took ill.

133
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,600
And the mastermind is...

134
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,600
Imperial Astronomer Yang Duojie.

135
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,080
Yes.

136
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:39,630
You're eloquent.

137
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:42,560
Why don't you explain to everyone?

138
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:43,030
Yes.

139
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:47,670
Your Majesty,

140
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,600
I

141
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,600
observed celestial signs at night

142
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,570
and discovered that
Imperial Guards Commander Zhao Wucheng

143
00:09:52,570 --> 00:09:53,960
harbored treasonous intentions.

144
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:54,720
Three days ago,

145
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,840
he deployed forces to raid the posthouse,

146
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,550
attempting to kill the Yan envoys.

147
00:09:58,550 --> 00:10:01,430
He then personally led men
to Mount Bei for an assassination.

148
00:10:01,430 --> 00:10:02,230
Fortunately,

149
00:10:02,270 --> 00:10:03,720
I made calculations

150
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,500
and anticipated this.

151
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:07,870
Not only did I rescue
the Yan envoys in advance,

152
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:09,500
but with their help,

153
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:11,560
I also foiled Zhao Wucheng's plot.

154
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:12,870
Although

155
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,550
we paid a heavy price...

156
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,700
Nevertheless,

157
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:21,880
to honor the Empress Dowager's desire
for peace talks

158
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,550
and not let it go to waste,

159
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:26,240
I request Your Majesty to proceed
with peace talks immediately!

160
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:26,770
Granted.

161
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,670
Summon

162
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:30,430
the Yan envoy!

163
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:50,880
But...

164
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:53,600
But we haven't gotten
to the bottom of this yet.

165
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,660
We can't trust the Yan people!

166
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,640
Your Majesty!

167
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,880
I, Prince Tu'er of Yan State,

168
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,930
pay respects to the Emperor of Xia!

169
00:11:14,110 --> 00:11:15,120
I never expected

170
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:16,630
that Prince Tu'er

171
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:19,120
would come in disguise himself.

172
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,440
To be frank,

173
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,720
I came under the Emperor of Yan's orders

174
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,360
to not just sign the peace treaty

175
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:28,950
but also to observe
your people's conditions and customs.

176
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,390
I concealed my identity earlier

177
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,700
to see

178
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,790
what Great Xia truly looks like.

179
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:36,150
So how did

180
00:11:36,330 --> 00:11:37,480
your investigation turn out?

181
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,230
Your Majesty upheld justice

182
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,360
at the Grand Longevity Banquet

183
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,480
and restored our innocence.

184
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,070
I believe

185
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,790
your example inspires your people
to be equally loyal and righteous.

186
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:46,150
The alliance between our two countries

187
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:47,600
will surely be a long-lasting one.

188
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,550
You flatter me.

189
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,360
Prince Tu'er,

190
00:11:50,830 --> 00:11:52,230
you are brave and mighty,

191
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:53,630
generous in your assistance,

192
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:54,630
and truly someone

193
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:56,500
I sincerely admire.

194
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,150
You're too kind.

195
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:01,320
Your Majesty is straightforward,

196
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,050
and I, Tu'er,

197
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,100
cannot be indecisive either.

198
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,080
I've brought my official seal.

199
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,390
Where is the peace treaty?

200
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:08,720
Where should I stamp it?

201
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:28,660
[Official Seal of Yan]

202
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:38,910
Lord Mu.

203
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,400
Your Majesty.

204
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,800
The Empress Dowager values you highly.

205
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,600
After court is dismissed,

206
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,070
you shall lead everyone

207
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,650
to convey this good news

208
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:53,770
of the successful peace talk
to the Empress Dowager.

209
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,600
I

210
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:58,780
obey your command.

211
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:01,080
Noble Consort.

212
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:04,000
I've just learned
a fashionable peony makeup style.

213
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,240
-Here. Have a try.
-No need.

214
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,150
I already applied makeup this morning.

215
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:06,840
Just try it.

216
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:09,840
Our Noble Consort is absolutely gorgeous.

217
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,120
If she wears heavy makeup,

218
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,240
it would only diminish her beauty.

219
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:15,480
Let me style your hair
in a simple cloud bun instead.

220
00:13:16,030 --> 00:13:16,490
No need.

221
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,600
Styling hair is too troublesome.

222
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,510
All these external things
are too superficial.

223
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:23,260
The Noble Consort values inner beauty.

224
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:26,390
Why not try my rose essence?

225
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:28,600
It also sparks passion.

226
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:30,810
Well,

227
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,240
that's hardly necessary.

228
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,320
It is necessary.

229
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:34,440
If we have

230
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:36,240
done anything wrong in the past,

231
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:38,440
please don't hold it against us,
Your Highness.

232
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,360
Not at all.

233
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,550
What do you mean by that?

234
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,550
Is our Noble Consort

235
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:42,910
a petty person?

236
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,050
Indeed.

237
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:48,710
No, no.

238
00:13:48,790 --> 00:13:50,120
That's not what I meant.

239
00:13:50,150 --> 00:13:51,320
Then what did you mean?

240
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,150
-She means...
-I—

241
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:54,360
you didn't understand what she meant.

242
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:56,260
What do you mean by that?

243
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,440
-What are they arguing about?
-Hey!

244
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,550
I didn't mean anything.

245
00:13:58,550 --> 00:13:59,150
What do you mean?

246
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:00,440
-Stop arguing.
-What's wrong with me?

247
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,200
All those things you did,

248
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:01,750
I remember them all.

249
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:02,270
All right, enough.

250
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,600
What do you mean by that?

251
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:04,910
You know perfectly well what I mean.

252
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:07,000
-Consort Shu is the most jealous one.
-I didn't.

253
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,600
Honestly speaking...

254
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,440
You two were arguing,

255
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:10,320
-why bring me into it?
-You guys are really interesting.

256
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:13,270
I didn't say anything about you,
why are you talking about me?

257
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,480
Noble Consort.

258
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:18,000
A few days ago you asked me
to refurbish the courtyard,

259
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,480
but

260
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,630
it's impossible

261
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,480
with just me alone.

262
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:25,800
-Refurbish the courtyard?
-I didn't!

263
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:27,770
Noble Consort,

264
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,390
please don't worry.

265
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:31,270
I excel at gardening.

266
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:34,190
On my way here, I noticed

267
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:35,630
the fish in this pond

268
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,850
are of poor quality.

269
00:14:36,990 --> 00:14:39,050
They should all be replaced with koi.

270
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:40,080
Kois!

271
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:42,240
Please leave the carpentry work to me.

272
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:44,440
After all, my grandfather
shares the same surname

273
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,360
as one of the greatest carpenters.

274
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,360
No need to work too hard!

275
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,870
I don't have many talents,

276
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,390
but I have plenty of money.

277
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,390
For this renovation,

278
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,720
there's no need to use
funds from the treasury.

279
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,250
Use mine.

280
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:54,480
Go on.

281
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:57,840
Thank...

282
00:14:58,910 --> 00:14:59,720
Thank you all.

283
00:14:59,870 --> 00:15:00,330
You see,

284
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,300
isn't the problem solved?

285
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,080
Come on.

286
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:08,900
Take a look.

287
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:09,490
That one!

288
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:10,630
Yes.

289
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:11,910
Fish it up.

290
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:20,800
What's going on?

291
00:15:21,650 --> 00:15:22,580
Why am I suddenly

292
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:23,870
so popular?

293
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:27,480
Once the Empress Dowager left,

294
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,340
you, as the most favored consort,

295
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,480
have naturally become

296
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,480
the palace's CEO.

297
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:34,960
But honestly,

298
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,080
compared to all this

299
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:38,910
cringe-worthy flattery,

300
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,510
I actually miss the days
when they hated me.

301
00:15:41,510 --> 00:15:42,150
Of course.

302
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:45,630
At least they weren't
tearing the place apart back then.

303
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:50,080
My fish!

304
00:15:50,710 --> 00:15:51,650
Stop!

305
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:54,500
It's over.

306
00:16:03,710 --> 00:16:04,840
I can't watch this anymore.

307
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:05,720
You can enjoy this on your own.

308
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,510
I'm going to look for Physician Xiao.

309
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:08,320
Don't leave!

310
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:09,480
Xie Yong'er!

311
00:16:09,670 --> 00:16:10,670
Reach down there!

312
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:14,110
Is no one
going to do something about this?

313
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:42,030
Greetings, Your Majesty.

314
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:55,630
Rise.

315
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:57,720
Her Majesty means

316
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,530
for all of you to rise.

317
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

318
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,980
Y-Your Majesty.

319
00:17:07,270 --> 00:17:08,329
Wh-What happened?

320
00:17:16,630 --> 00:17:17,990
Your Majesty,

321
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,060
His Majesty asked me to inform you

322
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:24,500
that the peace talks
have been successfully concluded

323
00:17:24,500 --> 00:17:25,900
and asks you not to worry.

324
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,460
If the Your Majesty cannot speak,

325
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:36,380
perhaps you could
write down your thoughts?

326
00:18:03,070 --> 00:18:03,870
Your Majesty?

327
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,680
Your Majesty?

328
00:18:05,380 --> 00:18:06,910
Are you okay, Your Majesty?

329
00:18:16,070 --> 00:18:16,750
What is this?

330
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,350
A shuttlecock.

331
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:18,070
What's it for?

332
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:18,800
For kicking.

333
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:19,550
For whom?

334
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:20,590
Us, of course.

335
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:21,880
Why?

336
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:23,950
I think

337
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:25,830
in this palace,
everyone's always comparing looks,

338
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:26,680
family background,

339
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,720
and His Majesty's favor.

340
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:29,850
The atmosphere is really unfriendly.

341
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,680
Besides,

342
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:32,350
throughout history,

343
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:33,890
the concubines in the palace

344
00:18:33,890 --> 00:18:35,350
have had short lifespans.

345
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:37,440
This situation is bad for everyone.

346
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:37,880
So

347
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:40,720
I've decided to introduce
shuttlecock kicking.

348
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,070
Let's channel the competitive spirit

349
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:43,930
into something more meaningful.

350
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:47,240
And redirect your energy

351
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:47,960
elsewhere.

352
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:49,880
Stop always scheming against me.

353
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,960
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

354
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,030
But...

355
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:52,600
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

356
00:18:51,270 --> 00:18:52,000
How do we...

357
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:52,830
Kick...

358
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:53,680
This shuttlecock?

359
00:18:52,970 --> 00:18:54,240
♪ Incredible ♪

360
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:54,960
It's simple.

361
00:18:54,690 --> 00:18:55,810
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

362
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,550
Let me show you.

363
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:57,280
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

364
00:18:57,450 --> 00:18:59,050
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

365
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,640
Watch carefully.

366
00:18:59,420 --> 00:19:00,580
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

367
00:19:01,020 --> 00:19:02,280
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

368
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:05,440
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

369
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,550
It's okay. I have more.

370
00:19:05,770 --> 00:19:07,360
♪ From day to night ♪

371
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:08,940
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

372
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:10,550
♪ From the present to the past ♪

373
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:11,830
♪ It's always you ♪

374
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:11,900
Come on.

375
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:13,280
Follow what I just showed you.

376
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,820
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

377
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,140
Have a try.

378
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:15,330
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

379
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,400
Come on, Consort Shu.

380
00:19:15,410 --> 00:19:18,330
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

381
00:19:18,650 --> 00:19:21,750
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

382
00:19:21,810 --> 00:19:23,710
♪ With you ♪

383
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:26,530
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

384
00:19:26,580 --> 00:19:28,140
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

385
00:19:28,210 --> 00:19:30,160
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

386
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:33,010
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

387
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:34,570
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

388
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:36,610
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

389
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,060
Good footwork!

390
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,320
It's okay.

391
00:19:41,790 --> 00:19:42,250
Come on!

392
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:47,030
It's boring

393
00:19:47,020 --> 00:19:48,490
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

394
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,510
to play shuttlecock alone.

395
00:19:48,510 --> 00:19:49,830
It's meant to be played together.

396
00:19:48,630 --> 00:19:50,330
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

397
00:19:51,110 --> 00:19:52,370
Come on, form a circle.

398
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,590
I'll pass it to you,
and you pass it to her.

399
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:57,350
I'll try.

400
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:04,700
♪ Incredible ♪

401
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:06,260
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

402
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:06,640
It's okay!

403
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:07,710
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

404
00:20:06,760 --> 00:20:07,560
There's more.

405
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,440
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

406
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:09,070
Come on.

407
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:10,980
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

408
00:20:11,450 --> 00:20:12,680
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

409
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:12,650
Your Highness,

410
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:14,220
can't we play somewhere else?

411
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:15,890
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

412
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,140
There's not much feather left.

413
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:17,810
♪ From day to night ♪

414
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,890
Chickens' lives matter too.

415
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:19,420
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

416
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:21,030
♪ From the present to the past ♪

417
00:20:21,070 --> 00:20:21,720
Sorry.

418
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:22,210
♪ It's always you ♪

419
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,190
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

420
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,780
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

421
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,270
But where can I find

422
00:20:25,810 --> 00:20:28,750
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

423
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:29,590
a spacious and deserted place?

424
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:32,160
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

425
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:34,240
♪ With you ♪

426
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:32,970
I got it!

427
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:37,030
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

428
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:38,620
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

429
00:20:38,690 --> 00:20:40,590
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

430
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:43,390
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

431
00:20:43,420 --> 00:20:45,050
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

432
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:47,000
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

433
00:20:51,050 --> 00:20:52,640
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

434
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:52,560
Noble Consort Wei,

435
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:54,290
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

436
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:54,720
long time no see.

437
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:57,960
Come.

438
00:20:58,030 --> 00:20:59,590
Move the heating brick inside,

439
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:00,590
closer to the bed.

440
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:01,750
Yes.

441
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:02,200
Yes.

442
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,550
Don't put it too close though,

443
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,510
it'll be too hot.

444
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:13,350
Madam Bei...

445
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:16,590
Foot bath water!

446
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:18,150
With hot water! Quick.

447
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,440
-Coming.
-Steady.

448
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:20,550
Mr. Bei.

449
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:22,810
-Don't fall.
-Mr. Bei.

450
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,530
In this cold winter,

451
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:27,140
water will freeze
if you drip it on the floor.

452
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,640
Please talk to me.

453
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:33,350
-Madam Bei.
-All right.

454
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:34,680
All of you may leave now.

455
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:37,640
Mr. Bei.

456
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:41,400
Mr. Bei!

457
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:49,880
I was wrong

458
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:52,840
for what I did this morning.

459
00:21:54,550 --> 00:21:55,480
But at that time,

460
00:21:57,550 --> 00:21:59,080
I truly had no other choice.

461
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,280
Do you know how much blood

462
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,210
you've lost?

463
00:22:03,030 --> 00:22:04,490
Not resting is bad enough,

464
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,750
but you dare to use
such dangerous methods.

465
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:08,680
You really don't care about your life.

466
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:09,440
I know

467
00:22:11,030 --> 00:22:12,070
you care about me.

468
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:16,350
But in that situation—

469
00:22:16,350 --> 00:22:17,280
What situation?

470
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,270
No matter what situation it was,

471
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:20,870
you shouldn't have
taken your life so lightly!

472
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,200
I've told you before,

473
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:24,640
Nan's child

474
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,400
is my child too.

475
00:22:27,820 --> 00:22:28,950
In this world, I have

476
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:30,840
no family and no relatives.

477
00:22:31,030 --> 00:22:32,880
The reason I protect you with all my might

478
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:34,830
is not for any grand cause
of the country or family.

479
00:22:34,830 --> 00:22:37,110
If you dare risk your life again

480
00:22:37,110 --> 00:22:38,310
for this darn throne,

481
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:39,030
I...

482
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:41,270
I will tie you up and take you away!

483
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:42,330
Do you understand?

484
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,000
I understand.

485
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:50,250
You care for me the most.

486
00:22:51,110 --> 00:22:51,590
I know.

487
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:56,150
Stop with these sweet words.

488
00:22:57,030 --> 00:22:57,830
They don't work

489
00:22:57,830 --> 00:22:58,290
with me.

490
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:10,950
Let me see!

491
00:23:10,950 --> 00:23:12,550
Is your wound hurting again?

492
00:23:13,590 --> 00:23:14,200
Mr. Bei...

493
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,260
This water is a bit hot.

494
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,700
You're so naughty!

495
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:24,090
Come, cover up properly.

496
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:25,460
Don't catch a cold.

497
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,470
Let me wash it for you.

498
00:23:29,790 --> 00:23:30,920
Bring your feet out.

499
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:38,130
Isn't the temperature just right?

500
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:40,110
Hot water drives away the cold.

501
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:49,750
Mr. Bei...

502
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,070
If only...

503
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:58,410
you and Wanyin had appeared earlier.

504
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:03,030
How wonderful that would have been.

505
00:24:09,270 --> 00:24:10,270
I want to play too.

506
00:24:21,190 --> 00:24:22,030
So impressive!

507
00:24:22,030 --> 00:24:23,290
Who would have thought

508
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:25,730
Noble Consort Wei would be such an expert?

509
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:28,270
Now that I've taught my apprentice,

510
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,600
I'm useless as a master—

511
00:24:30,040 --> 00:24:31,630
no wonder that's a saying.

512
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:32,430
She's so good.

513
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:33,290
Your Highness.

514
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:34,840
Are we returning to the palace

515
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,170
or going to His Majesty?

516
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:38,210
Let's go to His Majesty.

517
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:38,640
Yes.

518
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,080
The palace is so huge.

519
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,930
Why isn't there bike-sharing?

520
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:47,750
Isn't there a shortcut?

521
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:51,150
You're right!

522
00:24:51,270 --> 00:24:51,900
Like this?

523
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:07,160
Just admit it.

524
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:09,610
Seeing a bunch of women fighting for you—

525
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:12,770
you're secretly enjoying it, aren't you?

526
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:15,880
You're turning your head away?

527
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:17,010
What does that mean?

528
00:25:17,030 --> 00:25:18,790
I know men too well.

529
00:25:19,350 --> 00:25:20,440
You say no,

530
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:23,230
but inside you're probably delighted.

531
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:27,960
Fine.

532
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:30,920
I admit I'm jealous.

533
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:33,790
Sorry about that.

534
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:01,870
Let's go.

535
00:26:02,180 --> 00:26:03,240
What are you doing?

536
00:26:03,680 --> 00:26:04,680
I'm stuck.

537
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:05,800
Look at you.

538
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,670
You call yourself a hero?

539
00:26:07,750 --> 00:26:08,480
Hero?

540
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:10,500
More like your scapegoat!

541
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:16,030
Bai...

542
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:29,720
You don't snore, do you?

543
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:32,200
If you're afraid of noise,
go sleep upstairs.

544
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,030
Dream on.

545
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:05,490
How nice.

546
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:12,150
Your Majesty,

547
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,750
the Imperial Medical Bureau
is now focusing

548
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:17,150
entirely on treating the Empress Dowager,

549
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:19,240
but the results aren't promising.

550
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:21,830
If they can't handle it, you step in.

551
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:24,240
Make sure the Empress Dowager

552
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,640
can hold on for one month.

553
00:27:25,830 --> 00:27:26,380
Yes.

554
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,800
What do you plan to do now?

555
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:45,450
What's with that look?

556
00:27:45,750 --> 00:27:47,410
What kind of attitude is that?

557
00:27:48,840 --> 00:27:50,240
I know you don't trust me.

558
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:51,790
If it weren't for Yu Wanyin,

559
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:53,390
I wouldn't trust you either.

560
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:54,830
But I'm telling you,

561
00:27:54,830 --> 00:27:55,900
we're allies now.

562
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:57,970
If you don't tell me your plan,

563
00:27:58,270 --> 00:27:59,870
how can I cooperate with you?

564
00:28:06,430 --> 00:28:07,920
If the Empress Dowager doesn't die,

565
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:08,780
those factions

566
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:10,560
will keep their hopes alive

567
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:13,530
and won't immediately
side with Prince Duan.

568
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:14,590
You mean

569
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:17,510
you want to win over
the Empress Dowager's faction,

570
00:28:17,510 --> 00:28:19,040
stabilize the court first,

571
00:28:19,310 --> 00:28:20,590
then settle scores later?

572
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,790
You figured that out?

573
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:24,310
Not bad.

574
00:28:25,070 --> 00:28:27,510
Yu Wanyin said
you've only been here half a year,

575
00:28:27,510 --> 00:28:29,750
but the way you use these imperial tactics

576
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:31,950
doesn't look like you're acting at all.

577
00:28:33,510 --> 00:28:35,240
I'll take that as a compliment.

578
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,120
But your plan has one flaw.

579
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,720
There's a troublemaker
in the Empress Dowager's faction

580
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,450
named Mu Yun.

581
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,520
You must get rid of him first.

582
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,980
Or the plan won't work.

583
00:28:45,780 --> 00:28:47,140
The self-torture ruse,

584
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:48,840
the chain stratagem,

585
00:28:49,270 --> 00:28:51,270
and the counter-espionage tactic.

586
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,480
My brother

587
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:55,480
has really studied "The Art of War."

588
00:28:56,130 --> 00:28:58,260
He's even using double agent tactics.

589
00:28:58,590 --> 00:28:59,920
So what do you plan to do?

590
00:29:00,490 --> 00:29:01,090
Kill him?

591
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,600
That would be too easy on him.

592
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:09,290
Stir-fry him on high heat,

593
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,490
then simmer him on low heat.

594
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,770
Now that his cover's blown,

595
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,290
there are plenty of people

596
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:18,050
eager to deal with him.

597
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:25,730
I knew you were a tyrant.

598
00:29:30,850 --> 00:29:32,200
If there's nothing else,

599
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:33,400
I shall take my leave.

600
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:35,780
Farewell, my dear.

601
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:37,240
Tyrant.

602
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,740
How long do you plan to eavesdrop?

603
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:01,590
I wasn't just checking up on you.

604
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:03,450
Just wanted to take the shortcut.

605
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:08,120
Why do you look worse than this morning?

606
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:12,240
Before and after makeup
make a huge difference.

607
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,070
Liar.

608
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,690
Things didn't go well at court?

609
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:16,840
It went well—

610
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,270
very well.

611
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:20,410
What about you?

612
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:23,240
It's a long story.

613
00:30:31,350 --> 00:30:32,150
What's wrong?

614
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:34,270
How come
after being out for the whole day,

615
00:30:34,270 --> 00:30:35,290
you smell so good?

616
00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:39,830
Concubine He
just sprayed me with rose essence.

617
00:30:39,830 --> 00:30:42,610
Why not try my handmade rose essence?

618
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,600
It also sparks passion.

619
00:30:44,750 --> 00:30:45,510
No wonder.

620
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,880
It's driving me crazy.

621
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,520
I'm talking about serious matters.

622
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,920
This is a serious matter.

623
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:54,960
No.

624
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:56,310
Just one kiss.

625
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:58,720
Control yourself!

626
00:31:03,010 --> 00:31:04,250
Oh, one more thing—

627
00:31:09,830 --> 00:31:10,200
I...

628
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:12,480
Well...

629
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,380
How immoral.

630
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:24,800
How unethical.

631
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,310
No bottom line at all.

632
00:31:26,670 --> 00:31:27,810
Shameless.

633
00:31:28,440 --> 00:31:29,970
They know nothing but love!

634
00:31:30,720 --> 00:31:31,950
I won't be like you—

635
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:33,780
Your Highness!

636
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:36,160
Your Highness, are you alright?

637
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,940
Imperial Physician Xiao?

638
00:31:38,430 --> 00:31:39,280
Careful.

639
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:40,830
That hurt.

640
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:44,640
Why haven't you left yet?

641
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:46,680
I was thinking

642
00:31:46,830 --> 00:31:48,510
the palace is unsafe right now.

643
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,570
It's getting late,

644
00:31:49,570 --> 00:31:51,830
and it's not safe for you to return alone.

645
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:54,110
You've been waiting here for me?

646
00:32:08,680 --> 00:32:10,140
Imperial Physician Xiao,

647
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:11,770
you have something to say?

648
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,780
Imperial Physician Xiao.

649
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:20,290
I consider you a friend.

650
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,740
You can be yourself
in front of me.

651
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:25,180
Feel free to speak your mind.

652
00:32:28,260 --> 00:32:29,240
Consort Xie,

653
00:32:30,370 --> 00:32:31,480
there's something

654
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:32,810
I don't understand.

655
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:38,920
You're wondering

656
00:32:40,070 --> 00:32:40,790
how before,

657
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:44,310
I hated His Majesty
so much I wanted to abort his child,

658
00:32:44,310 --> 00:32:46,440
but now I'm running around everywhere

659
00:32:46,610 --> 00:32:47,940
trying to save his life?

660
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:49,350
Is that right?

661
00:32:55,830 --> 00:32:57,270
Imperial Physician Xiao.

662
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:57,870
I'm sorry.

663
00:32:58,750 --> 00:32:59,880
I lied to you before.

664
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:02,830
Your Highness, what are you doing?

665
00:33:04,590 --> 00:33:05,480
That child

666
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,700
was Prince Duan's.

667
00:33:08,110 --> 00:33:08,570
Prince—

668
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:14,170
Your Highness.

669
00:33:14,470 --> 00:33:16,230
You must never speak of this.

670
00:33:16,750 --> 00:33:18,590
If word gets out, it's a capital offense.

671
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:19,650
His Majesty knows.

672
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:20,120
He...

673
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,830
He knows?

674
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:29,410
Yes.

675
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:33,310
The power struggles at court

676
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:34,570
are no longer a secret.

677
00:33:35,550 --> 00:33:36,990
Before, to survive

678
00:33:37,070 --> 00:33:38,530
and for personal reasons,

679
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:40,500
I made some wrong choices.

680
00:33:41,310 --> 00:33:43,440
I've tasted backlash
of my own making.

681
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:47,440
Thankfully, His Majesty
and the Noble Consort are willing to help.

682
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:48,500
I've also realized

683
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:50,650
that Prince Duan is not a good man.

684
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:53,240
So rest assured, Imperial Physician Xiao.

685
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:54,170
I'm safe for now.

686
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:55,720
F-For now?

687
00:33:58,790 --> 00:34:02,390
What about after His Majesty
and Prince Duan settle their score?

688
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:06,030
Perhaps

689
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:09,310
I'll need to find a way to escape?

690
00:34:14,030 --> 00:34:15,350
Isn't it funny?

691
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:18,280
I wanted to possess the whole world,

692
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:21,449
but I'm trapped within these high walls.

693
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:23,630
I didn't even know

694
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:27,489
what the world looked like.

695
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,949
My dear, were you waiting for me?

696
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:55,150
Come,

697
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:57,190
My sir,

698
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,410
take your medicine.

699
00:35:02,490 --> 00:35:05,630
I've already taken the medicine
Imperial Physician Xiao gave me.

700
00:35:05,630 --> 00:35:08,070
I spent two hours brewing this,

701
00:35:08,670 --> 00:35:10,330
waiting for you to finish work

702
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:13,170
so you could drink
this cooling tonic right away.

703
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,230
I don't think that's necessary.

704
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:17,030
How so?

705
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:19,370
You're fighting all day long.

706
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:20,320
If you don't drink it,

707
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,380
you won't survive.

708
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,990
What was it I forgot to do?

709
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:28,280
The memorials!

710
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:28,810
Drink it.

711
00:35:34,590 --> 00:35:35,760
Fine, fine.

712
00:35:40,590 --> 00:35:41,720
That's more like it.

713
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:45,580
It's sweet?

714
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,280
Chrysanthemum with rock sugar—

715
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,480
of course it's sweet.

716
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,880
You're so good to me, my dear.

717
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,240
You...

718
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:05,620
Why are you still so irritable?

719
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,320
If you have energy, take it out on work.

720
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:08,700
Didn't you say there are
memorials left to review?

721
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:09,100
Go.

722
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,590
There are too many. I can't finish them.

723
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:12,070
CEO Dan,

724
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:14,200
I have to criticize you for this.

725
00:36:16,070 --> 00:36:17,590
Why do you think you're a bad actor?

726
00:36:17,590 --> 00:36:19,150
You don't read enough books.

727
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,920
No matter what industry you're in,

728
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:22,710
you require general knowledge.

729
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:23,940
Just a few memorials

730
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:24,920
got you good?

731
00:36:25,630 --> 00:36:26,490
If you can do it,

732
00:36:27,030 --> 00:36:27,830
then you do it.

733
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:31,310
I'm a seasoned corporate slave.

734
00:36:32,150 --> 00:36:33,410
This little bit of work

735
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:35,410
can be solved with some overtime.

736
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,480
Don't provoke me.

737
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:39,320
This little bit of work?

738
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,480
Eunuch An,

739
00:36:45,310 --> 00:36:47,310
bring up the unreviewed memorials.

740
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:52,380
Your Majesty,

741
00:36:52,670 --> 00:36:53,700
these just arrived.

742
00:36:53,700 --> 00:36:55,830
And there's still half more on the way.

743
00:36:59,670 --> 00:37:00,250
Well...

744
00:37:01,270 --> 00:37:03,070
I suddenly have something to do.

745
00:37:03,070 --> 00:37:03,800
My dear.

746
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,030
Don't make me

747
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,130
anxious and irritable.

748
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:14,530
Well...

749
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,230
is there overtime pay?

750
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:25,280
Grand Mentor Zhang

751
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:27,920
praised you 300 times,

752
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:31,370
but the main point
was to boast about his nephew?

753
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:34,290
There's flooding in J-Jiangnan.

754
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:35,730
[Grand Mentor Zhang's nephew]

755
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:36,340
S-So...

756
00:37:35,740 --> 00:37:37,190
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

757
00:37:37,150 --> 00:37:38,670
I-I think...

758
00:37:37,210 --> 00:37:38,830
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

759
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:39,510
Stop thinking.

760
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:40,470
♪ Incredible ♪

761
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:41,110
Listening to you gives me a headache.

762
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:42,090
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

763
00:37:42,510 --> 00:37:43,260
Drag him out.

764
00:37:42,570 --> 00:37:43,550
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

765
00:37:43,680 --> 00:37:45,280
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

766
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:45,650
Bring someone who can speak properly.

767
00:37:45,650 --> 00:37:46,810
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

768
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,630
Y-Y-Y-Your Majesty!

769
00:37:47,250 --> 00:37:48,510
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

770
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:50,400
Vice Minister Yang, Grand Commandant Lu,
and Minister Gou

771
00:37:48,890 --> 00:37:51,780
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

772
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:53,000
also submitted memorials

773
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,650
♪ From day to night ♪

774
00:37:53,190 --> 00:37:54,920
threatening to retire.

775
00:37:53,740 --> 00:37:55,170
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

776
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:56,830
♪ From the present to the past ♪

777
00:37:55,580 --> 00:37:56,320
Your Majesty!

778
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:58,760
[Grand Commandant Lu] [Vice Minister Yang]
[Minister Gou]

779
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:57,800
If this goes on,

780
00:37:56,930 --> 00:37:58,100
♪ It's always you ♪

781
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,070
a country will no longer be like a country,

782
00:37:58,550 --> 00:38:00,050
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

783
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:03,840
and I will be too ashamed
to accept the salary you provide.

784
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:01,760
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

785
00:38:01,790 --> 00:38:04,710
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

786
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:04,920
Then...

787
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:08,170
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

788
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:07,880
return it to me.

789
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:10,170
♪ With you ♪

790
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:10,880
The treasury happens to be low on funds.

791
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:12,950
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

792
00:38:11,150 --> 00:38:12,030
My lords,

793
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:13,880
you truly understand my concerns.

794
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,560
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

795
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:16,580
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

796
00:38:17,080 --> 00:38:19,430
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

797
00:38:19,070 --> 00:38:19,590
This

798
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,990
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

799
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:20,590
and these—

800
00:38:21,010 --> 00:38:23,140
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

801
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:22,480
they are ambiguous.

802
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,700
They're clearly fence-sitters.

803
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:27,000
Is that so?

804
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:30,360
Then let's send a gust of wind

805
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:32,200
to make them fall to our side.

806
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,070
The Minister of Revenue, Chen Danian,

807
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:35,150
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

808
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:35,430
is loyal.

809
00:38:35,250 --> 00:38:36,990
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

810
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,670
The Vice Minister of Works, Wei Hongyu,

811
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:39,000
is clever and decisive.

812
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:41,360
The Chief of the State Ceremonial Bureau,
Gu Tingzhi,

813
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,760
is rigorous and upright.

814
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,760
The Director of the Ministry of War,
Wu Jiadong,

815
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,230
is brave and loyal.

816
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:47,870
You are all promoted!

817
00:38:48,710 --> 00:38:50,480
Your Majesty is wise!

818
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:51,420
♪ Incredible ♪

819
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,760
Li Yunxi also submitted a memorial.

820
00:38:51,810 --> 00:38:53,070
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

821
00:38:53,390 --> 00:38:54,420
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

822
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:54,880
Didn't I tell him

823
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:56,210
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

824
00:38:55,030 --> 00:38:57,380
not to show up at this critical time

825
00:38:56,490 --> 00:38:57,780
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

826
00:38:58,150 --> 00:39:00,070
so people won't think of him
as an imperial loyalist?

827
00:38:58,160 --> 00:38:59,430
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

828
00:38:59,850 --> 00:39:02,710
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

829
00:39:01,960 --> 00:39:02,880
Don't worry.

830
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,630
♪ From day to night ♪

831
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:04,670
This time he has

832
00:39:04,670 --> 00:39:06,550
miraculously understood your intentions.

833
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:06,240
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

834
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:07,850
♪ From the present to the past ♪

835
00:39:07,920 --> 00:39:09,030
♪ It's always you ♪

836
00:39:08,110 --> 00:39:10,540
He knows you want him and those scholars

837
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:11,010
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

838
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:13,670
to appear resentful for not being valued.

839
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,670
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

840
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:15,640
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

841
00:39:14,110 --> 00:39:16,000
So even if Prince Duan gains power,

842
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:19,040
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

843
00:39:16,510 --> 00:39:18,400
he won't hold grudges against them.

844
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,190
So...

845
00:39:19,130 --> 00:39:21,120
♪ With you ♪

846
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,990
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

847
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:25,580
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

848
00:39:25,650 --> 00:39:27,550
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

849
00:39:28,080 --> 00:39:30,430
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

850
00:39:28,760 --> 00:39:30,460
Your Majesty is shortsighted,

851
00:39:30,460 --> 00:39:32,090
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

852
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,110
and you don't know how to use people.

853
00:39:32,110 --> 00:39:34,040
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

854
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:33,440
You are incompetent and foolish.

855
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,670
How inappropriate!

856
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:38,520
I said

857
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:41,120
there's no need to act too friendly.

858
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:43,580
But that's no reason for him to insult me!

859
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:46,170
